<h3>Sveiki, {{ name }}! Jūs rezervavote žvejybos laiką tvenkinyje <b>„DidelėsŽuvys.lt"</b></h3>

<b>Jūsų rezervacija {{ reservation.id }}:</b>
<br>Rezervuotas sektorius: <b>{{ reservation.sectorName }}</b>
<br>Rezervuota nuo: <b>{{ reservation.dateFrom|date('Y-m-d H:i') }}</b>
<br>Rezervuota iki: <b>{{ reservation.dateTo|date('Y-m-d H:i') }}</b>
<br>Žvejų skaičius: <b>{{ reservation.fishersNumber }}</b>
<br>Viso valandų: <b>{{ reservation.hours }}</b>
{% if reservation.house %}
    <br>Namelis: <b>užsakytas</b>
{% endif %}
<hr>
{% if not is_granted ('ROLE_ABONENT') %}
<div class="h4"><b>{{ 'Payment'|trans }}</b></div>
<div class="h6"><b>{{ 'You have 2 days to make payment.'|trans }}</b></div>
<div class="box-body">
    <div class="h5 font-weight-bold text-center">
        {{ 'Total payment'|trans }}: <b>{{ reservation.amount }} Eur</b>
    </div>
    <div>
        <span class="font-weight-bold">{{ 'Our billing accounts'|trans }}:</span>
        <br><span><b>AB SEB bank: LTXXX0XX0X0000XXXXXX</b></span>
    </div>
    <div>
        <span class="font-weight-bold">{{ 'Payment order must be indicated'|trans }}:</span>
        <br><span><b>{{ 'Reservation code'|trans }}: {{ reservation.id }},</b></span>
        <br><span><b>{{ 'Your email'|trans }}: {{ app.user.email }}.</b></span>
    </div>
    <hr>
{% endif %}
    <p>
        <span>{{ 'If you have any questions, please contact us'|trans }}:</span>
        <br>
        <span>email:</span> linas.kukulskis@gmail.com
        <br>
        <span>Tel.</span> +370 666 77777
    </p>

    <br><br>Laukiame atvykstant!

    <br><br><b><span>www.dideleszuvys.lt</span></b>
</div>
